WIZARDSHIP

Wizards (staff) build and maintain RiftsMUD. They are promoted from trusted
players by head staff and receive creator privileges in-game.

Wizard roles:
  Admin     full administration
  Domain    world building and zones
  Coding    systems and bug fixes
  RP        roleplay events and skills

Players cannot apply through a command. Demonstrate good roleplay, helpful
reports, and patience. Staff invite candidates when needed.

